description:
Have you noticed the constant propoganda being pushed in your face. Where I live, you can't drive more than a mile down the highway without seeing multiple electronic billboards projecting things like ""save lives, stay at home"" or ""cover your face in public."" This is rediculous and is clear propoganda. This nonsense needs to end.
